The paper deals with image classification using machine learning techniques, specifically for classifying human face shapes. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models such as Inception v3, which is a popular model in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of other classification methods such as SVM, MLP, and KNN, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also deals with image processing and analysis, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the need for expanding the labeled dataset, which is a common issue in neural network (cs.NE) research.
